content": "Jonah 2:8 (KJV)\r\nThey that observe lying vanities forsake their own mercy.\r\n\r\n\r\nLook into the law of liberty that perfects your works. Therein lies your needs and desires well met. Stop observing or considering lying vanities around you. Your mercies are near you, see them.\r\n\r\n\r\nBasically, the decisions you make must not be a direct result of fear, worry, anxiety, need, lack, or suchlike. The God of this world may arise but he has nothing in you. There is nothing in you that is similar to that which is of lack, fear, anxiety, stress, or suchlike.\r\n\r\n\r\nRemember, every thought that comes to you is not your own. Choose this day what to think. Choose who you will serve. Will you serve death or life? Glory or demise? Whose report will you believe?\r\n\r\n\r\nThe hand of God has been revealed to you and the peace of God overshadows your heart and mind. He keeps him in perfect peace whose mind is stayed on him (Isaiah 26:3)\r\n\r\n\r\nBlessings and peace to you all.", "author": "Prophet Namara Ernest", "date_posted": "2023-01-12T11:20:04Z", "status": "Published", "category": "Faith", "tags": ["Faith", "Thoughts"], "likes": 0, "comments": 0, "read_time": "", "image": "blog_images/pn_nu.jpg"}}, {"model": "blog.blogpost", "pk": 3, "fields": {"title": "Honor", "content": "1 Timothy 5:17 [KJV] Let the elders that rule well be counted worthy of double honour, especially they who labour in the word and doctrine.\r\n\r\n\r\nGlorious things are spoken of you holy saints of God, holy? Yes, sounds heavy for one with weaknesses and failures like you? Does it mean I am undefiled? You know better than anyone! That wouldn't be you by a mile. \r\n\r\n\r\nBut there is great news, be holy as I am holy, says the Lord. This indicates that you decide to be holy as he is. It's not a power from without that is christened on you after years of hard Christian living.\r\n\r\n\r\nTo be holy is to be SET APART FOR THE MASTER'S USE. Can you really decide that? Emphatically yes. Is it possible to determine within that, you are going to be ready for divine purpose and use? Yes you can. \r\n\r\n\r\nWe are once again in a special time emphasised by the holy spirit a few years ago when he intended to bring back honour in his house by Prophet Elvis Mbonye.\r\n\r\nThis long watered down way of God is a deep benchmark for the workings of the holy ghost in the church and certainly in our midst.\r\n\r\n\r\nI pray that this finds your heart unfazed and unhardened by the issues of life because these have been satan's weapon against the workings of the Spirit amongst the church of the Lord Jesus. \r\n\r\nA hardened heart if not checked quickly grows weary of finding he who is life and light. \r\n\r\n\r\nOne who is a true seeker will find himself shrouded by tests and trials daily, but the love for Jesus my friends will get you through.\r\n\r\nA hardened heart is dangerous for your walk in salvation. Notice that satan will take advantage of delayed expectations to draw you away from your walk.\r\n\r\n\r\nThis is when many Christians begin coming up with all sorts of ideas in a bid to soothe their desires. They will attempt all sorts of things including changing locations, being offended in the house of God, even changing congregations not knowing it's the Lord who plants you in a congregation and so on.\r\n\r\n\r\nThe long watered down way of honour in the kingdom in many ways is the answer. The kingdom of God operates in hierarchy and ranking. It's the unschooled men in the spirit that do not realise this truth. \r\n\r\nThey believe, we are all the same. One will have a dream here and there and think himself to be spiritual or a Prophet. \r\n\r\n\r\nThere are men who you walk with in this life like Abraham and you are blessed. In fact you can even be blessed to his level and think you are the same. Lot got so blessed that he even had more things than Abraham and he thought to himself I don't need Abraham anymore let me go to a better country, little did he know the source of his substance.\r\n\r\n\r\nFriends, Jesus said, I am the tree and ye are the branches, remember? Without me you can do nothing. Weren't there people in his day who seemed to be doing something? Of course they were, but were they in him? Of course not.\r\n\r\n\r\nOne time I met a lady now gone from our ministry who was going through something and immediately my eyes were open to deal with it and she turned and addressed me as Pastor and that was it. In her eyes I didn't have the solution for her problem but I actually had it. \r\n\r\n\r\nTo honour is not lip service. \r\n\r\n\r\nIsaiah 29:13 [KJV] Wherefore the Lord said, For as much as this people draw near me with their mouth, and with their lips do honour me, but have removed their heart far from me, and their fear toward me is taught by the precept of men: \r\n\r\n\r\nIt is written that let him who rules well be counted worthy of double honour. 1 Timothy 5:17 [KJV] Let the elders that rule well be counted worthy of double honour, especially they who labour in the word and doctrine.\r\n\r\nThere in lies our solution. It has to be something extraordinary.\r\n\r\n\r\nIt's not time to nod your head in awe of great anointing. It's often about digging deep financially in response to the unction of destiny upon a man of God with whom you are assigned to walk with for your own good.\r\n\r\n\r\n1 Corinthians 9:11 [KJV] If we have sown unto you spiritual things, is it a great thing if we shall reap your carnal things? \r\n\r\n\r\nLove and peace to you all.", "author": "Prophet Namara Ernest", "date_posted": "2025-08-08T09:28:03Z", "status": "Published", "category": "Faith", "tags": ["Honor", "Giving"], "likes": 0, "comments": 0, "read_time": "", "image": "blog_images/pn_nu_3.jpg"}}, {"model": "blog.blogpost", "pk": 4, "fields": {"title": "Fans or Followers", "content": "“Follow me, and I will make you fishers of men\" is the first interaction we see in the Word concerning the great commission.\r\n\r\nThe idea of role modeling/ being heart knit with what one is trying to accomplish as a mission or goal or destiny or purpose, no matter how noble is predicated on this principal, follow me and I will make you do the things I do. e said that those who believe in me will do the works that I do and greater (John 14:12) . And therefore it is not farfetched to expect to do the works of Christ and even greater.\r\n\r\n\r\nThe greatest difference between a fan and a follower is his knowledge of the purpose to which he is called to follow or zealous about. We have turned into a community of \"fans of Christ\" instead of followers of Christ. We claim to be followers of Christ while casually depicting traits of fans and wonder why we are never turning into his image. The follower must be fully expectant to turn into that which he is following. \r\n\r\n\r\nA football fan no matter his love for the club or players in the game is not expecting that one day he will score a jaw dropping \"rabona\" goal himself but doesn't mind being the \"tell all\" of how fantastic the goal was and how the goalkeeper had no chance in the world to save it. \r\n\r\n\r\nWhen we talk of financial dominion, what really comes to most of our heads is a Ferrari or Lamborghini etc yet those are effects of money but financial dominion is really money with a mission beyond self-gratification. People who own worldwide news corporations don't start them to benefit their relatives. They have a mission bigger than their immediate family and friends. \r\n\r\n\r\nPeople who own dominant airline companies don't start them to have a good cockpit view of the sky and those who own international chain hotels don't start them to have a nice bed to spend the night. you get the point, they already have a mansion at home. That's the difference between a fan and a follower of our message. A follower understands mission and he connects at the level of purpose.\r\n\r\n\r\nOne prolific writer known for his distaste of face masks told me how he met a fan of his writings and told him to his face. \" I love your posts and never miss any and even know your distaste for face masks but as for me I will put it on\" and he smiled and fist bumped and they walked on. That is exactly who a fan is, he likes what he reads only to the extent that his mind is stimulated and thank God it's that way or else we will have too many wannabes. \r\n\r\n\r\nThe point is, nobody expects a fan actually to be turned into the image of the leader or \"star\" he is in love with. But sadly this has infiltrated the church. People go for fellowship or church or meet to worship one they don't intend on being like. They are fans and not followers. However, Christ fully intended on turning his followers to become like him, saying;\r\n\r\n\r\nJohn 12 (KJV)\r\n\r\n¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯\r\n\r\n²⁴ Verily, verily, I say unto you, Except a corn of wheat fall into the ground and die, it abideth alone: but if it die, it bringeth forth much fruit.\r\n\r\nThe idea behind his ministry was to turn his followers into himself, as many as believed in his name were given power to become sons of God.\r\n\r\n\r\nThis is exactly what is missing in the house of God. We have too many fans who have forgotten the mission and purpose to which we are called/ the reason we do what we do.\r\n\r\nToo many are subscribed to different prayer groups or fellowships and churches as fans and not followers. They will tell you what's happening in every church or fellowship in town, like the football fan, they don't expect and don't intend to ever know the end of the matter to which they claim to follow. They are secret admirers who never reveal their identity because the cost of following to the end of the matter is too high.\r\n\r\n\r\nThe trouble with such people, they lose their conviction faster than they got it, they are\r\n\r\nenjoying a journey and have forgotten the destination. Some sing and have forgotten why they sing, some preach and cannot fathom why they preach, some usher and are not nearly aware of the cause, some give and sow and have forgotten why or worse they have mixed up their conviction on why they started doing so in the beginning.\r\n\r\n\r\nMy call for you today is to remember why you are doing what you are doing or else your spiritual life grows cold, be doer's of the word and not hearers only thereby deceiving yourselves.\r\n\r\nYou who sings do you remember why you started in the first place?\r\n\r\nYou who ushers do you remember your first convictions or they have since morphed?\r\n\r\nYou who gives, do you remember your initial convictions on the matter or they have since changed? \r\n\r\nThere is always a starting point to all relationships the scripture calls it \" first Love\"\r\n\r\nRevelation 2 (KJV)\r\n\r\n¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯\r\n\r\n² I know thy works, and thy labour, and thy patience, and how thou canst not bear them which are evil: and thou hast tried them which say they are apostles, and are not, and hast found them liars:\r\n\r\n³ And hast borne, and hast patience, and for my name's sake hast laboured, and hast not\r\n\r\nfainted.\r\n\r\n⁴ Nevertheless I have somewhat against thee, because thou hast left thy first love.\r\n\r\n\r\nShalom! Much love to you.\r\n\r\nSee you on Sunday 28th. Be there.\r\n\r\nBlessings", "author": "Prophet Namara Ernest", "date_posted": "2025-08-08T09:29:17Z", "status": "Published", "category": "Faith", "tags": ["Discipleship"], "likes": 0, "comments": 0, "read_time": "", "image": "blog_images/pn_nu_4.jpg"}}, {"model": "blog.testimony", "pk": 1, "fields": {"name": "Felixe Butera", "image": "testimonies/felix.jpg", "quote": "From 7 years of total inactivity and unfruitfulness to a company being sought after by an international brand. Talk about RESTORATION IN CAPITAL LETTERS. I am a witness to the raised standards, and I accord innumerable honor to the vessel of God, Prophet Namara Ernest.", "role": "Events Manager"}}, {"model": "blog.testimony", "pk": 2, "fields": {"name": "Peter Wisdom", "image": "testimonies/CLF_9302.JPG", "quote": "Three years ago, I had no clear prospects in life. Today, I am a Software Engineer. The difference? The anointing upon Prophet Namara.", "role": "Software Developer"}}, {"model": "blog.testimony", "pk": 3, "fields": {"name": "Carol Ernest", "image": "testimonies/cn1.jpg", "quote": "I invented the cure to HIV, cancer and a new remedy for TB", "role": "Clinic Assistant"}}, {"model": "blog.heroslide", "pk": 2, "fields": {"title": "Prophet Namara Ernest", "subtitle": "Prophet Namara Ernest", "image": "hero_pics/prop_pgblikD.jpg", "description": "A Prophet of God sent to preserve and protect the people of God", "created_at": "2025-08-25T15:54:44.087Z", "updated_at": "2025-08-26T10:35:07.997Z"}}, {"model": "blog.heroslide", "pk": 3, "fields": {"title": "First Born Fellowship", "subtitle": "Every Saturday", "image": "hero_pics/choir_2.jpg", "description": "Join Prophet Namara Ernest every Saturday and partake of the unique grace not only to teach that imparts a tangible reality of God's supernatural realm.", "created_at": "2025-08-25T15:55:43.983Z", "updated_at": "2025-08-26T10:41:56.434Z"}}, {"model": "blog.heroslide", "pk": 4, "fields": {"title": "Spirit World", "subtitle": "Every Monday", "image": "hero_pics/pr_gold.jpg", "description": "Listen to Prophet Namara Ernest on the Spirit World every Monday as he boldly and fearlessly digs deeper into the infinite realm of God", "created_at": "2025-08-25T15:56:27.806Z", "updated_at": "2025-08-26T10:58:14.580Z"}}, {"model": "blog.heroslide", "pk": 5, "fields": {"title": "Mission: Protect and Preserve My People", "subtitle": "Prophet Namara", "image": "hero_pics/prn_cr.jpg", "description": "A prophet of God sent to preserve and protect the people of the Lord", "created_at": "2025-08-25T15:56:58.427Z", "updated_at": "2025-08-26T10:45:09.173Z"}}, {"model": "mediafiles.audio", "pk": 1, "fields": {"title": "The Spirit World Program 09.06.2025", "speaker": "Prophet Namara Ernest", "date": "2025-06-09T11:48:18Z", "active": false, "description": "The weekly life-giving broadcast", "drive_url": "https://drive.google.com/file/d/1ZQ6eySvGrOEmyKYP_atGDUoGWqdtw2M3/preview"}}, {"model": "mediafiles.audio", "pk": 2, "fields": {"title": "The Spirit World Program 02.06.2025", "speaker": "Prophet Namara Ernest", "date": "2025-06-02T11:50:46Z", "active": false, "description": "Life Giving Broadcast", "drive_url": "https://drive.google.com/file/d/1FCGFB4dkCjQ6Seh9nITbw74ju1kTeKWj/preview"}}, {"model": "mediafiles.audio", "pk": 3, "fields": {"title": "Spirit World Audio 05.05.2025", "speaker": "Prophet Namara Ernest", "date": "2025-05-05T11:51:35Z", "active": false, "description": "Life Giving Broadcast", "drive_url": "https://drive.google.com/file/d/1kiSXKOF1BpWzCjBhhUegjKqJg95jjmCX/preview"}}, {"model": "mediafiles.audio", "pk": 4, "fields": {"title": "The Spirit World Program 04.08.2025", "speaker": "Prophet Namara Ernest", "date": "2025-08-04T11:52:14Z", "active": true, "description": "Life-giving broadcast", "drive_url": "https://drive.google.com/file/d/1bACREj1hsHue9NYY8iLhEIM2puXlssJ5/preview"}}, {"model": "mediafiles.video", "pk": 18, "fields": {"title": "The Modi & Trump Meeting: What You Need to Know", "description": "", "embed_id": "V85KJHciV9M", "source_url": "https://www.youtube.com/embed/V85KJHciV9M?si=WBM1m9aOIXI-_5qf", "duration": "30", "views": "400", "category": "Prophecy", "date_posted": "2025-08-07T14:09:28.860Z"}}, {"model": "mediafiles.video", "pk": 19, "fields": {"title": "The Shocking Current Situation in Argentina", "description": "The current situation in Argentina is shocking, to say the least. Protests have erupted across the country, with violent clashes between demonstrators and security forces. But what's driving the protests, and what does the future hold for Argentina? In this video, we'll delve into the latest news and updates from Argentina and the revelation of Prophet Namara as revealed in prophecy.", "embed_id": "4qz9A1l9ya0", "source_url": "https://www.youtube.com/embed/4qz9A1l9ya0?si=W_39Na_WfGjgXUPW", "duration": "40", "views": "67k", "category": "Prophecy", "date_posted": "2025-08-07T14:16:31.907Z"}}, {"model": "mediafiles.video", "pk": 20, "fields": {"title": "Uganda's Shocking Cyclone: A Warning for Us All", "description": "Uganda's Shocking Cyclone is a warning for us all. In this video, we examine the cyclone's shocking impact and what it means for Uganda's future. With Prophet Namara Ernest sounding the alarm, it's clear that this is not just a local crisis but a warning for us all.", "embed_id": "tXZ_p5Emw2w", "source_url": "https://www.youtube.com/embed/tXZ_p5Emw2w?si=32WMSRPOue_42MdX", "duration": "45", "views": "3.4k", "category": "Prophecy", "date_posted": "2025-08-07T14:17:35.872Z"}}, {"model": "mediafiles.video", "pk": 21, "fields": {"title": "Sam Omala: What You Need To Know About His Death", "description": "Security personnel are grieving the loss of Sam Omala, the former Director of Police Operations in what was known as the Kampala Extra region. Omala became a well-known figure in Kampala, often recognized for his role in quelling riots and public demonstrations.", "embed_id": "zgPpNCWPhz0", "source_url": "https://www.youtube.com/embed/zgPpNCWPhz0?si=-b6hKef_rb1Ka08h", "duration": "67", "views": "8.9k", "category": "Prophecy", "date_posted": "2025-08-07T14:18:16.841Z"}}, {"model": "partners.partner", "pk": 1, "fields": {"firstName": "Peter", "lastName": "Wisdom", "email": "r@w.com", "phone": "07563563826", "message": "I am committing to UGX 100,000 weekly", "submitted_at": "2025-08-06T18:06:57.849Z"}}, {"model": "partners.partner", "pk": 2, "fields": {"firstName": "Peter", "lastName": "Wiseone", "email": "wise@d.com", "phone": "34567897", "message": "I am commiting to ugx 100,000/=", "submitted_at": "2025-08-14T13:32:37.655Z"}}, {"model": "partners.partner", "pk": 3, "fields": {"firstName": "James", "lastName": "Martin", "email": "jmarti